('Pehak', 'Rice, Meat, Onion, Ginger, Garlic, Green chilies, Soy sauce, Salt, Oil', '1. Cook rice and let it cool. 2. In a pan, heat oil and sauté chopped onions, ginger, and garlic until golden. 3. Add meat and cook until browned. 4. Add green chilies, soy sauce, and salt, and stir-fry until combined. 5. Mix in cooked rice and serve hot.'),
('Apong', 'Rice, Fermented rice, Water, Salt', '1. Mix fermented rice with water and salt to form a dough. 2. Knead the dough until smooth. 3. Shape into small balls and serve.');